{"tid":322404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得自己係零","createTime":"2017-07-14T19:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T19:06:19.000Z","uid":61199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b96b38a810b469e59aa3d853f5bbd3a1b6f44079","tid":322404,"uid":61199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:00:36.000Z","msg":"書讀唔好 野做唔掂<br />\n又黑人憎 肥矮毒柒窮中晒<br />\n又成日得罪人<br />\n又懶醒<br />\n心地又唔好 憎人富貴厭人窮<br />\n鐘意既人又配唔起佢<br />\n啲野錯完又錯 好似冇腦咁<br />\n仲要錯埋啲唔錯得既野<br />\n<br />\n到依家先發自己毫無價值<br />\n我好想死<br />\n救我<br />\n我好辛苦<br />\n點先可以改變"},{"pid":"56ea6e2f89b7da70edf0d7431ffa2434d19a506a","tid":322404,"uid":124192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:02:10.000Z","msg":"如果住私樓仲有價值"},{"pid":"701985a224b34ffa8a8e27dec0efadd22251422c","tid":322404,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f461f6cb1ce14ffca93aa315df1d324e8cce7b89","tid":322404,"uid":61199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>零乘一百都係零</blockquote><br />\n岩阿<br />\n就係知道先咁難受"}]}